WorkItem.Description:
This is a feature request but the DataFieldBinding field allows to bind columns to indexed properties:
The DataGridTemplateColumn does not have this field, and relies on the Template to do it.
Â 
So dynamically created columns like the code below would not be possible to create with the DataGridTemplateColumn :
for (int j = 0; j < Values.Count; j++)
{
    DataGridTextColumn column2 = new DataGridTextColumn();
    column2.Width = 30;
    column2.Header = "Value";
    column2.DataFieldBinding = new Binding(string.Format("Values[{0}]", j));
    msDataGrid.Columns.Add(column2);
}
